{"id": 5694, "title": "Ticket #5694: SUBMIT_ATTRS can't set JobLeaseDuration to an expression", "description": "<blockquote>\n<code>SUBMIT_ATTRS</code> can't set <code>JobLeaseDuration</code> to an expression.\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>bug1 When the code that parses the submit file looks it doesn't see <code>JobLeaseDuration</code> and so it sets a default that ends up overriding the value from <code>SUBMIT_ATTRS</code>.\n\n<p></p></li><li>bug2 if use <code>JOB_LEASE_DURATION</code> in <code>SUBMIT_ATTRS</code>, then the submit file parsing code fails unless the value of <code>JOB_LEASE_DURATION</code> is an integer. it cannot be an expression.  It also stuffs a attribute named <code>JOB_LEASE_DURATION</code> into the job ad, which is harmless but confusing.</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-May-26 16:57:56 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nthis fix needs to go into submit_utils in the master branch also.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2016-Jun-01 11:43:43 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>This change looks good.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-May-31 11:26</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b6edfe610eeaba1d4ccaa8ffd7a650a7f3658d21\">[48447]</a></span>: version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2720\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2720'); return false;\" title=\"condor_submit creating files with $$([])\">#2720</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5310\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5310'); return false;\" title=